Package: ProcessMapping
Title: Creates process diagrams using a structured process description
Version: 1.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Tim",
           family = "Perkins",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "tim@theperkins.se",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5080-1418")))
Description: Plots a process map in the style of SIPOC, UPN, swimlane or tree from structured 
    data typically stored in Excel. It calculates coordinates for process steps and calls 
    DiagrammeR to  parse and render as a graph
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
